==Ancient Greek==

===Pronunciation===
*[[ἄγγελος]] / aggelos / ang'-el-os

===Etymology===
*From αγγέλλω aggellō (probably derived from {{GG|71}}; compare {{GG|34}}; to bring tidings); a messenger; especially an “angel”; by implication a pastor: - angel, messenger.

